Class ListNode<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ListNode<T>

  • public class ListNode<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a node in the linked list. NOTE: This class is a modified version of the class in Deitel and Deitel's Java How To Program Early Objects, 10th Edition
